 such systems through the dynamical\nassembly is exceedingly rare, leaving this system a dilemma hard to account for\nwith the currently accepted paradigms of BBH formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 18:40:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2020 04:36:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2020 00:55:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-08"}
