etics that would result in\nvariable severity of illness. Understanding how this genetic variation may\nalter the response to SARS-CoV-2 infection is critical to develop successful\ntreatment strategies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 19:17:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 May 2020 12:20:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-20"}
