zation of\nchromite, especially upon the system hydridization, cooling, oxidation and\nmagma degassing. Our model may be applied for quantitative prediction of\nchromite crystallization and formation of the terrestrial mantle-crust\ntransition zones and mantle represented by chromitites and dunites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 May 2020 15:29:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-15"}
