\ntransit detection is confirmed, e.g. with CHEOPS photometry, DMPP-1 would be a\nfirst-rate target for JWST spectroscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 May 2020 15:54:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-27"}
